    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Appointment
    Appointment class which creates an object to describe the Appointment for the Patient and Staff.
    Billing
    Billing class which creates an object to describe the Billing for the Patient.
    Doctor
    Subclass Doctor which extends the abstract class Staff and implements the Schedulable interface.
    Patient
    Subclass Patient which extends Person class and implements the Treatable and Schedulable interfaces.
    Person
    Abstract Superclass Person which defines the common attributes and methods for any person at the Clinic.
    Receptionist
    Subclass Receptionist which extends the abstract class Staff and implements the Schedulable interface.
    Salary
    Salary class to create a salary object for the Staff object instances.
    Staff
    Abstract subclass Staff which extends the Person class.
    Treatment
    Treatment class which creates an object to describe the Treatment for the Patient.
